cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.CY, cs.SY, cs.CR 

The paper discusses the connectivity landscape of the Internet of Things (IoT) and machine-to-machine (M2M) communications, which are primarily related to networking and communication technologies. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Additionally, the paper also discusses the technology features, expected performance, and standardization developments, which are related to information theory (cs.IT), cybersecurity (cs.CY), control systems (cs.SY), and cryptography (cs.CR).
